title: LF Mid/Support for a Dia2+ DACH region Team.

embed.title: mash on Twitter
embed.description: LF Players to join a new DACH region LoL team. @GlitchFeelings We will be aiming for @ESLGermany Division 2, as well as joining the @SummonersInnDE League. See the image below for requirements. Send me a DM if you're interested or have questions!

body:
We're looking for players, especially a midlaner or supporter to join a regional team, aiming for ESLM 2nd Division and SINN League.
Requirements are in the Tweet. 
We need a mid/support for a full team, but also willing to tryout Top/JG/AD!
German residency is a +

Thank you! DM on Twitter please, I'm not active here!{{summoner:3}}
